  "texts": [
    "For the number of chunks, we tested integer values between 2 and 10 to observe performance changes with different chunk sizes.",
    "For the overlapping sentences, we tested two settings: 0 or 1.",
    "If set to 1, one sentence overlaps between consecutive chunks; if set to 0, there is no overlap.",
    "Breakpoint-based Semantic Chunker We tested two hyperparameters: the type of breakpoint threshold and the threshold amount.",
    "Sentences were split into chunks when the distance between consecutive sentences exceeded a predefined threshold."
